	<div class="tab-panel active" id="tab1">
		<p><h3>Gliscor (Japanese: Glion)</h3> is a dual-type Ground/Flying Pokémon introduced in Generation IV. It evolves from Gligar when leveled up holding a Razor Fang during the night. In Pokémon Legends: Arceus, it evolves from Gligar when exposed to a Razor Fang during the night, instead. </p>
		<p>Info from: bulbapedia.com</p>
